      <h3>2. 100% Full Loan</h3>
      <p>Most banks will only lend you 70% or 80% of the equipment value. That means you still need to find RM50,000 for a RM250,000 machine. With us, we can cover the full cost.</p>

      <h3>3. No Age Limit on Used Machinery</h3>
      <p>This is where we are different. Banks often refuse to finance machines older than 5 or 10 years. In manufacturing, a well-maintained 15-year-old machine can still work perfectly. We finance used equipment regardless of age, as long as it is in good working condition.</p>

