      <p>While we like to see an established business, we are more interested in your current performance and future potential. If you have a clear plan for how the machine will make money, we want to hear it.</p>

      <h3>Can I buy from a private seller?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Whether you are buying from an authorized dealer or another factory owner who is upgrading their line, we can facilitate the financing. We will handle the inspection and documentation to make it smooth for both parties.</p>

      <h3>What are the repayment terms?</h3>
      <p>We offer flexible terms ranging from 1 to 5 years. We will sit down with you and figure out a monthly installment that fits your factory's typical monthly income.</p>

      <h2>3 Steps to Get Your Machinery Financed</h2>

      <p>We believe in keeping things simple. You have a factory to run; you do not have time for 10 meetings.</p>

