        <li><strong>Step 2: The Documents.</strong> Send us your basic company info and the last few months of bank statements. We do not need a 50-page business plan.</li>
        <li><strong>Step 3: The Approval.</strong> We review and give you a "Yes" or "No" quickly. Once approved, we handle the payment to the seller and you get your machine.</li>
